75; J Pinero (Spain) 73, 69, 68, 74, 74.
Other scores included: 361 - R Russell (Longniddry) 70, 73, 71, 76, 71. 362 - S
Henderson (King's Links) 70, 76, 68, 75, 72. 364 - W Guy (Buchanan Castle) 73,
74, 72, 72, 73.
MATTHEW LINDSAY
