<TEXT>
Skye decimals
DESPITE my address I am actually from Skye and like Amelia Simonini I live at
an apparently unusual address when I return to Skye during the college holidays.
Several houses in Skye have addresses such as 3/4 of 2, !s of 3, etc. This
number refers to the share of the croft land and not the houses. Our house is
on !s a croft while our neighbour, several acres away, has the other  !s .
As for some of the Rev William Shackleton's other queries, Skye has just as
good a postal delivery service as many other parts of the country. And,
finally, 3/4 of 2 in decimals is 1.5.
Lindsey M Duncan,
40 Beech Avenue,
Langlee, Galashiels.
</TEXT>
